This, Bill...
this is money, yeah?

01:04:03.464 --> 01:04:06.591
You know there's more
to this than money.

01:04:20.940 --> 01:04:23.650
- Sorted, Jonny?
- Sorted, Maggie.

01:04:23.860 --> 01:04:26.653
