Jonny.

01:04:30.449 --> 01:04:33.743
I know you can see
the bigger picture, yeah?

01:04:33.953 --> 01:04:35.704
Yeah.

01:04:36.914 --> 01:04:38.248
This house, eh...

01:04:38.457 --> 01:04:41.251
